{"tid":626380,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經] 真係好懷念以前既ONLINE GAME 魔力、天翼、神話、亂、古惑仔....","createTime":"2018-04-12T05:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T06:00:29.000Z","uid":36994,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a149395ad50f81af29b7307fd1d61d4fe259ea42","tid":626380,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"由細細過五年級開始玩魔力，<br />\n番到學校總有幾堆人講唔同既GAME，<br />\n又魔力、又RO、又天翼、又龍族。仲有好多好多。<br />\n直到中學我堅持玩魔力，其他同學已經玩緊古惑仔..武林群俠傳(網龍GAME)<br />\n跟住3D game就好hit 神話, <br />\n<br />\n特別係有隻叫 亂ONLINE 果期D中學同學玩到痴曬線。<br />\n<br />\n依家d rpg 壽命好短...好快收皮.. 好似黑沙咁, 又要掛機又成..<br />\n之前入左水藍玩左陣.. 已經拎唔番之前去里洞, 過海學亂射果種感覺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我介紹我女朋友玩, 佢仲話低b.. 其實我玩既唔係隻game 玩既係青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d8b92906c922e649857f4f575512d0cc6e1984","tid":626380,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"唔唔"},{"pid":"8d91c24bc50a9c7c9ff917d7e32c074bc94f2ce7","tid":626380,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61900985cac113316d75ed4d6953a90bb074f645","tid":626380,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:53:36.000Z","msg":"金庸1"},{"pid":"bf148f9931805b47b0852010b83fe3b72068d93f","tid":626380,"uid":110761,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"玩過最好嘅online game係sd<br />\n沒有之一"},{"pid":"d96854852f80918e5bdcb8eeb0db5a2e27b49714","tid":626380,"uid":164167,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"無人想知呢D舊game <br />\n食下雞好過"},{"pid":"d760312f0e974ea1c7f987e702bafb9587c70fd